A lesser, chaotic neutral god of arctic beasts, cold, northern barbarians, and winter, Vatun was imprisoned by priests of his rival Telchur 700 years ago.
There are rumors that he may be imprisoned by devils, probably Belial, Telchur's ally. 
His only allies are Llerg and his brother Dalt.
Sources: Frostburn, http://www.wizards.com/rpga/downloads/LG_Deities.zip, Living Greyhawk Gazetteer, Living Greyhawk Journal no. 3 - "Gods of Oerth", Player's Guide to Greyhawk, The Scarlet Brotherhood